  • Method Details

    • getServerIp

      void getServerIp()
      Ask the user the IP of the server it wants to connect to

    • getName

      void getName()
      Ask the user the username it wants to use

    • setName

      void setName​(java.lang.String name)
      Once the name is validated by the server, it is stored in the player manager
      Parameters:
      name - the name given and validated

    • setIdFirstWorker

      void setIdFirstWorker​(int id)
      Store the id of the first worker of this player (1-3-5)
      Parameters:
      id - the id of the first worker

    • chooseNumberPlayers

      void chooseNumberPlayers()
      If there isn't any match on the server, the player is asked to create a new one So this method ask the player how many players it wants this match to have

    • placeWorker

      void placeWorker​(boolean firstWorker, int[] possiblePositions)
      Ask the player where to place his workers at the start of the game
      Parameters:
      firstWorker - true if the player hasn't place any worker before
      possiblePositions - all the possible positions enumerated from 0 to 24 (A0 is 0, A1 is 1, ... , E4 is 23, E5 is 24)

    • chooseWorker

      void chooseWorker​(int workers)
      Ask the player which of its workers to use in this turn
      Parameters:
      workers - the list of the workers that can be moved

    • chooseMovement

      void chooseMovement​(int[] movements)
      Ask the player in which of the possible cells it wants to move the previously selected worker
      Parameters:
      movements - list of the possible movements

    • chooseBuilding

      void chooseBuilding​(int[] buildings)
      Ask the player in which of the possible cells it wants the worker to build
      Parameters:
      buildings - list of the possible cells to build in

    • buildDome

      void buildDome()
      Ask the player if it wants to build a dome or a normal building in the previosly selected cells

    • showGods

      void showGods​(java.lang.String[] god, java.lang.String owner)
      show the god's description and name
      Parameters:
      god - first index contains name of God, second index contains Its description
      owner - is the name of the owner of the God.

    • doItAgain

      void doItAgain​(Message.MessageType moveAgain)
      used if god power allows to move/build again
      Parameters:
      moveAgain - only equals to MOVE_AGAIN or BUILD_AGAIN

    • buildBefore

      void buildBefore()
      used by god powers if you want to build before moving

    • showTurn

      void showTurn​(java.lang.String object)
      shows whose turn it is
      Parameters:
      object - the name of the player whose turn it is

    • getName

      void getName​(java.lang.String object)
      shows request of get name
      Parameters:
      object - is the question asked by the server "what is your name"/"name is already being used"

    • buildOtherWorker

      void buildOtherWorker()
      asks if player wants to build with the other worker in certain conditions (Poseidon God power)

    • printLoser

      void printLoser​(java.lang.String object)
      shows who just lost the game
      Parameters:
      object - loser of the game
